Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:37.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,After 'em! Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:39.67,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Hurry up!\N- What the-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Five billion bucks and all untraceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How about a money shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:11.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hot! Very hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:16.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Just burry me, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:29.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's dump it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:31.59,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're very convincing, but they're all counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They are? They can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:40.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Why would a government-run casino\Nhave counterfeit money?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're Gothic bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gothics? I thought that was just a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:48.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Nope, but you wouldn't expect to\Nsee them in a state casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:51.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jigen, that should be our next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:53.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to spread the wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:55.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Get this funny money out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of principality of Cagliostro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're the smallest country in the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Their population's only 3,500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah, and you're sure this is where the\NGothic bills are coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They have a nickname for this place in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's the Black Hole of Counterfeiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Why the Black Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They say anyone who comes around here\Nsnooping is never seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's quite a scary story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Scares me right to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:16.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And the spares totally bald, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's really not helpful, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.45,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Who're we helping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:32.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:42.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shoot the tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:43.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Those aren't normal tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:17.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now things are getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:20.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This time I'm giving 'em the good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.81,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:09.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,She's passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Her car's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take the wheel, Jigen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:21.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:41.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:42.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Let me go!\N- Hey, knock it off. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:35.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We're going to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:37.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Look down there and you'll see.\NLook down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now please hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:18.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yo, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You look rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.55,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Where's the bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:19.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All of that for some girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:33.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Where have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You take a look at that ring and now\Nyou're acting all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Woah, take it easy, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:19.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are we doing at this old castle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's just like the crest that was on that ring, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This place wasn't deserted that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:51.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Just passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Are ya tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be the palace of His\NHighness the Prince, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's still the Prince's palace, and it's\Nnot open to tourists or outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If it's still the Prince's palace, why\Nthe heck is it all hollowed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There was a big fire seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:17.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ever since the passing of the Prince and his wife,\Nit's been left to fall apart, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the Prince kind of like a king?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You guys don't have a ruler any longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's a region, so apparently it's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So don't you linger, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:28.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:31.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You went and got all grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Quit playing dumb, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Stop you're choking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's going on, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:33.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:38.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:39.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll talk, I'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's the castle of the regent Count Cagliostro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:10.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,On the other side of the aqueduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's that boat from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So the bride is in that castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's a sluice gate where it's docked,\Njust like it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, you've broken into that castle before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:33.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I went in there over 10 years ago to learn\Nthe secret of the Gothic bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I was one naive little punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I got a royal butt kicking, so I skedaddled\Nand hightailed it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Who the heck flies an autogyro these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:16:59.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go find an inn or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:02.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:04.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That was careless of you, Jodot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,My apologies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Her ladyship was being fitted for her wedding gown,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,and the men were not present at\Nthe time, your Eminence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,She's in the North Tower now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:42.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The drugs have put her into a sound sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Foreigners?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:52.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:54.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm told it was two men, strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,While she tried to escape, they came to her aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:18:01.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Find them, and dispose of them as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:07.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:11.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The ring is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Get me Jodot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:51.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's written in the old Gothic alphabet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:56.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gothic, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,"With light and shadow as one once more,\Nit shall surely be restored."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:02.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,"1517."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The year is in Roman numerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So this thing's over 400 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ooh, looks yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You seem awfully preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This? It's just an old ring I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:15.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:16.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It has the crest of Lady Clarisse on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh? Clarisse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,See, that's her in that photo up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's from when she was little, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,She came back from the convent yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's a fine young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:31.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The convent?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I thought you gentlemen were here for the big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lady Clarisse is going to marry the Count this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:39.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why all of these sightseers were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I don't envy Lady Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:46.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The Count has a bad reputation for being a playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Playboy? Like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How about tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.42,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.38,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,She's a Capricorn, he's a Libra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that guy was one of the Count's spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.18,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Leave some.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:06.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The Count wants both the girl and the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:08.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:12.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me that girl we\Nsaw today was the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Thought I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:34.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,With light and shadow as one once more,\Nit shall surely be restored, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Do you think it is a treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:39.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:22.09,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, who invited these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:37.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're bulletproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:42.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:22:58.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:01.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.87,0:23:02.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Creep-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:11.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yeesh, that was something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:13.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly wasn't the welcoming committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:15.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Down the rabbit hole we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:17.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Think they're trying to tell us something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:53.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,These didn't turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:56.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lately the quality's been very disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:58.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,My apologies, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.23,0:24:02.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But our quality control can't keep up with mass production.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:05.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Redo all of these and don't miss our delivery date.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:07.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:14.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Forgive me excellency, I have failed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.11,0:24:16.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The rats have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:18.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:22.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jodot, what is that paper on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.03,0:24:26.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:27.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,When did he do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.82,0:24:29.68,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:31.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's a warning from Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.28,0:24:32.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.07,0:24:34.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.32,0:24:36.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.03,0:24:40.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,To the count of lust and greed,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.19,0:24:42.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking your bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.07,0:24:45.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Expect me soon, signed Lupin the Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:48.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's good news, Jodot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.03,0:24:49.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.44,0:24:54.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let us wait then for Lupin to come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.69,0:25:39.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You got here quick, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.90,0:25:43.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.73,0:25:50.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Goemon's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.03,0:25:52.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And so are the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.23,0:25:52.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.90,0:25:53.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Go take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.93,0:25:54.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:25:58.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.78,0:26:01.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Japanese police cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.94,0:26:03.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's Zenigata.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.11,0:26:03.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.19,0:26:07.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All personnel, disembark.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:09.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Pull in!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.94,0:26:15.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now our cast of characters is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.53,0:26:18.49,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot, hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.98,0:26:28.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for interrupting your meal, Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.07,0:26:37.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm Zenigata of the International\NCriminal Police Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.53,0:26:39.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm here because you received a notice from Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.48,0:26:44.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah, that petty thief who claims
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.36,0:26:46.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,to be the grandson Arsene Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.82,0:26:49.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Does Interpol always disturb people's breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.07,0:26:50.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,over such trivialities?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.86,0:26:52.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Excellency, don't underestimate Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.61,0:26:55.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If he says he'll come, he'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.48,0:26:57.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Your ceremony's in five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.40,0:27:00.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I must insist that you allow us\Nto inspect your castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.61,0:27:05.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We have police in this country too,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.65,0:27:08.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,though we refer to them more elegantly\Nas the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:10.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You rang, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.69,0:27:13.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gustav, I want you to cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.28,0:27:14.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,with this Japanese officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.11,0:27:15.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.28,0:27:16.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.07,0:27:17.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.44,0:27:20.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me why you think Lupin
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.11,0:27:21.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,would be after your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:26.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Well, it's your job to investigate\Nthese matters, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.73,0:27:28.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.03,0:27:36.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Do you think it wise to have\Nthat Inspector roaming the castle, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.82,0:27:37.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.78,0:27:39.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I have friends even inside Interpol.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.94,0:27:41.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't fear, he'll be leaving soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.40,0:27:48.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's Zenigata, truly a child of pre-war Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.61,0:27:49.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,One determined bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.32,0:28:01.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.98,0:28:03.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, do not take another step.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.28,0:28:04.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.98,0:28:06.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.34,0:28:13.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If you prefer to stay alive, don't wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.15,0:28:15.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Be sure to pass that on to your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.23,0:28:23.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir, we're picking up anti-personnel radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.78,0:28:25.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm, something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.69,0:28:27.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's too small a country for defenses like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.03,0:28:32.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.23,0:28:34.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't go, it's not what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.11,0:28:36.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's a woman involved, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.61,0:28:38.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,but there's more to the story, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.07,0:28:40.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Is there anything special about this ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.03,0:28:42.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We'll know that once we get the girl back
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.90,0:28:44.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,from that creepy old man, the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:48.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, my magnum couldn't dent the monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.90,0:28:51.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,but with your blade and this anti-tank rifle,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.03,0:28:55.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey Lupin, did you find a way in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:57.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Nope, this place is a fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:28:58.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,a network of lasers and radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.07,0:29:02.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No kidding, we're gonna need a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.53,0:29:04.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So is that why you called Zenigata?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.40,0:29:05.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.15,0:29:09.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you got it, you're as sharp as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.32,0:29:12.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You are going to fight fire with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.23,0:29:19.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This is the castle of Cagliostro.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.15,0:29:23.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We're here and this Roman aqueduct is still in use
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.32,0:29:25.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,and it's our only way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.86,0:29:28.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They use the aqueduct to draw water
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.86,0:29:30.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,from the lake into the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.28,0:29:35.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good news since there won't be\Nany laser cannons underwater, an easy in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.82,0:29:37.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Goemon, you're the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.36,0:29:47.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.70,0:29:49.42,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Told ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.78,0:30:00.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here's the first hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:03.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:06.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey! Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.36,0:31:27.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's the Clock Tower's machinery room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.90,0:31:30.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I really hope Lupin made it through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.36,0:31:59.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm. What's that windmill do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.48,0:32:02.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gustav told us it brings water\Nup into the castle, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.36,0:32:06.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Where's that water come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.94,0:32:08.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It comes out in a fountain up in the battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.78,0:32:10.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Come with me now! \N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.06,0:32:36.79,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.98,0:32:37.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,New orders from Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.53,0:32:39.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We're to withdraw and return at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.82,0:32:42.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What? That's totally ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.11,0:32:44.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna verify this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.36,0:33:00.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What? But, but Lupin left one of his warning notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.44,0:33:02.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm? The Count called.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.23,0:33:07.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he made a stink. We're\Npolice officers, not his lackies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.32,0:33:10.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We gotta job to do-- Hello? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.53,0:33:14.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this up with the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.36,0:33:20.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, show me the way, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.36,0:33:27.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm here to talk to the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.19,0:33:29.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me? Let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.23,0:33:31.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No admittance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.65,0:33:35.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Inspector, only the trustworthy are\Nallowed past this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.36,0:33:38.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You telling me the ICPO can't be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.57,0:33:41.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I believe you've been ordered to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.90,0:33:43.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please take your men and leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.82,0:33:46.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How in the world did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.78,0:33:50.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We can deal with Lupin without the help\Nof you foreigners. Now leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.32,0:33:56.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand. We'll pull out for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.44,0:33:56.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.44,0:34:04.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.36,0:34:10.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Were you just talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.36,0:34:15.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You idiot, that was Lupin. \NHe just disguised himself to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.32,0:34:18.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What good are those muscles if you\Ncan't even spot a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.65,0:34:21.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.36,0:34:23.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't let Lupin get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.36,0:34:31.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.36,0:34:34.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We have you, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.07,0:34:35.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.36,0:34:39.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm not Lupin! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.65,0:34:43.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're attacking the inspector.. Everybody\Nput down those guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.78,0:34:51.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Toodle, see you, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.94,0:34:55.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.48,0:35:15.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.78,0:35:34.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It appears that we caught someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.36,0:35:42.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Idiot should have left when he still had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.69,0:35:43.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Where are the guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.32,0:35:46.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gustav. What is he doing leaving his post?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.78,0:35:50.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- You stay here. \N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.19,0:35:54.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.78,0:35:58.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gustav, call off this insanity immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.61,0:36:02.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Are you blind and dumb? Lupin played\Nyou like a fiddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.23,0:36:04.20,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.36,0:36:11.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.15,0:36:20.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So Lupin snuck in, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.36,0:36:22.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,My shame is beyond words, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.94,0:36:27.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Tell the police officers that their inspector\Nwent back ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.90,0:36:29.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,People vanish all the time while traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.44,0:36:30.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.36,0:36:55.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.44,0:36:59.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Fujicakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.36,0:37:00.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.98,0:37:04.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Seeing a woman engrossed in her\Nwork is a beautiful sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.40,0:37:06.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You've made it this far in here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.61,0:37:08.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's been almost a year, and that's all you can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.32,0:37:10.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You know I searched everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.57,0:37:14.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, what you're really searching\Nfor is the bride, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.65,0:37:17.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah, can't fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.44,0:37:20.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you where she is if you promise\Nyou won't get in the way of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.32,0:37:23.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Of course, of course. You know I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.69,0:37:26.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. She's at the top of the North Tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.36,0:37:29.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,but I don't think there's any way\Nyou'll ever get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.98,0:37:34.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.65,0:38:04.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yikes. What a lousy place to be locked up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.36,0:39:14.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.69,0:39:25.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.31,0:39:35.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.36,0:41:02.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.36,0:41:05.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I am a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.36,0:41:07.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Did you say thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.61,0:41:13.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Miss Bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:16.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You helped me. I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.53,0:41:18.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.36,0:41:27.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You came to give me this back when you know the\NCount would kill you if he found you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.40,0:41:30.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Aiming for a prize you're being aimed\Nat, it's all part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And once the job's done, I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.68,0:41:35.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The job?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.41,0:41:39.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If I had anything of value here I\Ncould offer you, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.86,0:41:44.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But I'm a prisoner. Oh. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.32,0:41:54.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This time I seek a priceless treasure sealed in the\Ntop of a tall tower by an evil sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.23,0:41:55.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.40,0:42:00.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Would you please allow this thief\Nto steal you away from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.36,0:42:02.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Steal me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.90,0:42:10.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,To rescue jewels and riches that\Nare trapped inside a safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.32,0:42:16.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, to stop a forced marriage and release the girl\Nto run in the grassy fields of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.90,0:42:20.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All of these jobs are perfect for a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.19,0:42:23.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You've come all this way to free me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.32,0:42:40.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.94,0:42:45.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But I don't think you noticed how terrible\Nthe House of Cagliostro truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.28,0:42:50.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please, just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.36,0:43:00.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.73,0:43:03.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This lovely sweet girl believes in\Nthe powers of the wicked evil
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.44,0:43:06.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,sorcerer, yet somehow refuses to believe\Nin the powers of the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.28,0:43:11.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If the girl would only believe, the thief\Ncould take to the skies above.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.15,0:43:15.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He could drink up all the water in the\Nlake if only she'd believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.78,0:43:43.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But for now, this'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.36,0:44:19.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.69,0:44:23.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, show the lady the respect she deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.36,0:44:37.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all this way\Nto deliver the ring, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.11,0:44:40.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I am so deeply honored by this welcome party, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.40,0:44:43.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's touching, but you're going away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.28,0:44:47.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? You think it'll be that\Neasy to get rid of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.36,0:44:50.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, please! Leave him alone! Don't hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.11,0:44:53.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay, Missy. You've just\Ngot to believe in the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.06,0:44:56.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.48,0:45:01.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, the Monsieur is right here. Don't worry.\NHe'll be back real soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.36,0:45:05.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So, what's the game gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.11,0:45:09.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Tearing you apart would be too easy,\Nbut I'd rather not sully
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.28,0:45:12.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,the bride's room with the blood of an\Ninconsequential sneak-thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.73,0:45:15.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Call me names if you want, but you're\Ngoing to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.40,0:45:18.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It was nice of you to drop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.36,0:45:29.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That hole leads to a foul Hell of a place\Nthat no one has ever escaped from.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.48,0:46:03.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So innocent, and yet you've attracted\Na man to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.48,0:46:06.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's the Cagliostro blood at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.61,0:46:10.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You deserve to be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.73,0:46:12.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Murderer! You're an inhuman monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.48,0:46:18.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How true. My hands are covered in blood,\Nbut yours are no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.03,0:46:22.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,For generations, my family has served\Nin the shadow of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.07,0:46:26.45,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,overseeing schemes and assassinations\Nto support this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.95,0:46:29.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! You disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.98,0:46:33.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You can't tell me you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.19,0:46:37.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You are of Cagliostro blood as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.98,0:46:42.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The same ancient blood of the Goths that flows\Nthrough my veins flows through yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.90,0:46:48.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, Clarisse, it's been over 400 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.57,0:46:51.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The two houses of light and shadow\Nhave been kept apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.36,0:46:56.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,With light and shadow as one once more,\Nit shall surely be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.15,0:46:59.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This is the golden goat of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.23,0:47:04.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Your ring, bearing the silver goat,\Nwill become one with mine
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.65,0:47:07.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,to restore the hidden treasure of our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.82,0:47:11.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, I totally heard that. A marriage\Nfor treasure, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.94,0:47:12.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.65,0:47:16.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Count on a counterfeiting Count for all\Nhis words and deeds to be a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.40,0:47:19.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The girl is a very kind hearted, wonderful young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.11,0:47:24.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.86,0:47:25.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.15,0:47:28.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the girl's belief in him,\Nhe can even take to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.65,0:47:31.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir Thief will come and steal you away for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.98,0:47:32.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.98,0:47:33.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.57,0:47:35.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Blast him, it's the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.49,0:47:37.31,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.36,0:47:41.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Count, you listen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.57,0:47:46.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I got the real ring. You even lay\Na finger on that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.03,0:47:48.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And here's what I'll do to your precious ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.94,0:47:51.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.84,0:48:08.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Dump me down a sewer, will you? Well poo to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.65,0:48:09.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.65,0:48:10.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.15,0:48:11.01,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.44,0:48:14.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No man could possibly exist down there for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.07,0:48:16.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If we leave him, he'll die for certain, Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.36,0:48:18.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That little weasel still has the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.69,0:48:20.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll check immediately, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.94,0:48:24.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You'll see. I'll have that petty little thief\Nof yours, flayed and quartered.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.36,0:49:44.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Over 400 years of killing, killing and more killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.86,0:49:45.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.73,0:49:54.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,1904, Japanese Army scout Inosuke Kawakami died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.65,0:49:56.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Avenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.10,0:50:08.71,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.40,0:50:14.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lupin! You! You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.90,0:50:17.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops, how are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.57,0:50:20.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll be asking the questions. How'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.44,0:50:22.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, I dropped in just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.36,0:50:28.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been walking for quite a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.61,0:50:31.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I don't want pity for a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.36,0:50:34.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I think we should take it easy. There's\Nno way out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.19,0:50:37.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,May I borrow this seat, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.65,0:50:41.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops. Got a light?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.82,0:50:43.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lupin, what's the deal with the skeletons?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.57,0:50:46.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like a gravesite.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.82,0:50:48.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take a look at the wall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.44,0:50:49.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.48,0:50:57.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This... this message...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.36,0:51:01.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,May you rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.15,0:51:06.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I figured this was no ordinary castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.78,0:51:08.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What could be worth going this far to keep a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.57,0:51:10.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.78,0:51:15.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, it's why Fujicakes is here. Hope she\Nfares better than us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.94,0:51:19.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Anyway, grumbling about it won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.11,0:51:20.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Good night, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.57,0:51:40.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Man, would you look at the time. See anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.94,0:51:41.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.73,0:51:44.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do but wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.36,0:53:25.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What's keeping them?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.90,0:53:27.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Master Jodot, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.36,0:53:32.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Ah, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.36,0:53:38.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Heave! Heave!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.07,0:53:40.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Toodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.36,0:53:43.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't leave us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.36,0:53:52.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.19,0:53:55.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.90,0:54:04.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What kind of place is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.73,0:54:12.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.82,0:54:18.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,These are 10,000 yen bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:20.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And so's this whole heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.36,0:54:24.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Exceptional quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.40,0:54:26.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Check it out, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.23,0:54:30.10,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh? These marked bills are from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.10,0:54:35.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Pounds. Dollars. Franks. Rubles.\NRupies. Pesos. Crowns. Lira.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.07,0:54:37.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Whoa.\NEven Chinese Yuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.23,0:54:39.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They got the whole world covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.65,0:54:43.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah, printing counterfeits.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.61,0:54:45.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, this is the castle's secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.57,0:54:47.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.32,0:54:48.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The home of the Gothic bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.36,0:54:51.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Better than the real thing, some would even say.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.65,0:54:56.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Fake money's been a shadowy player in every European\Nupheaval since the Middle Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.40,0:55:00.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It brought down the Bourbon dynasty\Nby helping fund Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.98,0:55:05.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And in 1927, it was the trigger behind\Nthe Great Depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.98,0:55:08.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The hidden player on the dark side of history?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.65,0:55:10.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gothic bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.19,0:55:14.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And anyone who tried to find its source never escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.27,0:55:22.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I had heard the rumors before, but I'd never imagined\Nit was the work of a sovereign nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.28,0:55:25.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.57,0:55:27.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it, you can't just unsee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.19,0:55:28.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.19,0:55:30.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No good cop could ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.98,0:55:34.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How about a truce, just until we get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.36,0:55:37.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Okay. But I won't aid in a better criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.19,0:55:41.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Once we've escaped, you're under\Narrest for good this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.78,0:55:42.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.98,0:55:44.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, pops, why don't we shake on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.40,0:55:48.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's collusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.07,0:55:49.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.28,0:55:58.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ms. Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.11,0:56:00.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I've come to say goodbye to you while I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.94,0:56:04.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.82,0:56:08.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I was hired to be milady's handmaiden, the\Nonly other woman in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.82,0:56:13.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But the truth is, I'm a spy hunting\Nfor the secret of this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.36,0:56:17.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I planned to stick around longer, but Lupin showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.65,0:56:19.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He'll mess up everything, so I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.40,0:56:21.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You know that gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.94,0:56:23.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Better than I wish I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.36,0:56:26.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sometimes friends, sometimes adversaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.90,0:56:28.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I suppose we've even been lovers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.69,0:56:32.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He's an infamous womanizer. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.90,0:56:33.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Did he leave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.36,0:56:36.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.36,0:56:43.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Smoke's coming from the trap door.\N- Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.36,0:56:48.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.89,0:56:53.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Movement.\N- Finally, some action.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.36,0:57:09.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sir! The fire started down in the printing plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.57,0:57:11.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Then get down there and put it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.19,0:57:11.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.69,0:57:14.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And shut that door! You all go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.03,0:57:17.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jodot, you have failed once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.36,0:57:26.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shake a leg, Pops! We're gonna have\Ncompany here real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.23,0:57:28.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Evidence! I need evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.29,0:57:36.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Curse that Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.78,0:57:41.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Find him! I'm sure he's still in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.36,0:57:47.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for? Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.36,0:57:54.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Lupin's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.19,0:57:56.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.56,0:58:05.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.86,0:58:10.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's Monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.69,0:58:13.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.53,0:58:14.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin! And Zenigata?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.36,0:58:23.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're after the autogyro.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.88,0:58:28.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.86,0:58:32.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You can reprimand me later, sir! He's\Nafter Lady Clarisse! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.99,0:58:41.85,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.36,0:58:51.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm from Interpol!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.52,0:58:53.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Pops, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.28,0:58:56.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come on, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.36,0:59:04.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sayonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.03,0:59:07.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops! I'm gonna make a quick pit stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.94,0:59:09.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna kidnap her?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.53,0:59:10.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's non-profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.36,0:59:18.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.58,0:59:39.37,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's bulletproof glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.36,0:59:43.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We can't open it! Please just go without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.36,0:59:50.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.48,0:59:54.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here, you take the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.69,0:59:58.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What? Hey, Lupin! I've never done this before!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.10,1:00:00.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.23,1:00:03.06,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.57,1:00:04.14,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.61,1:00:07.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Your chariot awaits, milady. Fujiko, some rope.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.36,1:00:08.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't boss me around!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.90,1:00:17.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.42,1:00:36.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There you are! You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.30,1:00:43.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Pops! Put it down over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.12,1:00:44.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You think I'm not trying, you maniac!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.04,1:00:52.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All right, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.90,1:00:57.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Easy!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.03,1:01:16.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.36,1:01:20.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't you move, you meddling rat!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.69,1:01:28.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Fujiko, I will look forward to\Ninterrogating you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.53,1:01:31.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jodot, go ahead and finish off Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.65,1:01:31.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.36,1:01:35.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, please don't shoot him! If you kill\Nhim, then I shall die as well!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.78,1:01:37.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.36,1:02:00.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I admire your attitude, Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.73,1:02:06.85,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take back the ring from him and come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.68,1:02:10.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If you marry me, I will agree to spare Lupin's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.48,1:02:16.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Or you can both die here and now. The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.36,1:02:28.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The ring, Monsieur, let me have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.48,1:02:32.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Clarisse. You just can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.98,1:02:35.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,In his collar, he always hides things under there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.36,1:02:38.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Darn you, Fujiko!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.36,1:02:56.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here is the ring. Now spare this man and miss Fujiko's\Nlife, or I swear to you, I will throw it in the lake!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.90,1:03:00.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You have my word. Put on the ring and come to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.69,1:03:01.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shall I shoot?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.78,1:03:02.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wait till I have the ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.92,1:03:19.75,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shoot them down!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.36,1:03:27.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You horrible liar! You gave your word!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.36,1:03:31.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They've seen the printing presses. I'd\Nnever let them leave here alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.44,1:03:40.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's in my hands at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.15,1:04:00.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, let's just say you owe me one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.42,1:04:02.34,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.48,1:04:09.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now we gotta go without getting in on the fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.03,1:04:16.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We're going down!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.44,1:04:17.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jump for it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.36,1:04:32.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Again I have cut a worthless object.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.36,1:04:37.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, come back here so I can arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.98,1:04:45.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Right, this could be a very big problem.\NIf anyone finds out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.40,1:04:48.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,These fake bills, I've never seen anything like them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.44,1:04:53.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let us take action! We have this\Nindisputable evidence!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.73,1:04:57.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I saw it myself! Counterfeit printing\Npresses lined up!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.53,1:04:58.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We understand that, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.90,1:05:03.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This is a very sensitive political problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.73,1:05:07.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Our jurisdiction at Interpol is limited\Nonly to international crimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.69,1:05:10.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? This is clearly criminal activity!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.44,1:05:11.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.36,1:05:17.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're sovereign state and a member of the UN. Interpol\Ncan't conduct a forced investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.78,1:05:19.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,In addition, the situation is not in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.69,1:05:24.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Did you see the picture that's on the front\Npage of every newspaper in the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.57,1:05:29.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The Count who bravely protected his bride against\NLupin who tried to abduct Princess Clarisse?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.36,1:05:33.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And he apparently had an accomplice disguised as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.44,1:05:35.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That was all me, I was there!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.73,1:05:38.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's a problem. It makes it seem as though\Nyou were colluding with Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.19,1:05:41.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Did you forget? I told you what happened!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.07,1:05:45.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The issue is, who is the public gonna believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.48,1:05:46.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They won't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.11,1:05:50.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The Count supposedly has a lot of political\Nfriends in the west.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.15,1:05:53.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That alone could be a big problem for some countries.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.28,1:05:58.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Especially for a certain country that placed\Na huge order for fake American bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.36,1:06:01.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And I suppose these fake rubles weren't\Nordered by your CIA.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.23,1:06:05.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, stop! This is not the place\Nfor international disputes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.15,1:06:10.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, please! Each country will decide\Nhow to deal with the Gothic bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.36,1:06:21.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we're prepared to mobilize. Ready to\Ndepart for the Principality of Cagliostro.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.53,1:06:24.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We're not going, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.36,1:06:29.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,As soon as they find a suitable replacement for\Nus, we'll be taken off the Lupin case.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.32,1:06:31.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Prepare to return to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.86,1:06:43.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.44,1:06:46.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here's some food.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.28,1:06:47.20,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Great. Thanks, pal.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.22,1:06:48.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How's your friend doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.69,1:06:52.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,His fever seems to have gone down. Thanks\Nto you operating on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.36,1:06:55.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's that dog you should really give thanks to.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.19,1:07:00.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That old dog is friendly to no one, but he\Nwon't budge from that man's side.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.94,1:07:03.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If not for that, I probably wouldn't\Nhave offered you folks shelter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.86,1:07:15.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.23,1:07:17.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He's finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.65,1:07:19.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.57,1:07:25.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jigen. Goemon. Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.90,1:07:27.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Long time? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.07,1:07:30.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,His wounds have temporarily impaired his memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.36,1:07:34.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Karl? How come you're not with\Nyour mistress today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.94,1:07:38.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How in the world could you possibly\Nknow that dog's name is Karl?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.40,1:07:43.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I thought the only ones still around here who knew\Nit were myself and the lady Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.40,1:07:44.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.36,1:07:49.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So, Karl, the name of your mistress\Nis Clarisse, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.36,1:07:51.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.69,1:07:57.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.19,1:08:00.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jigen, tell me what day it is. How\Nmany days has it been?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.28,1:08:02.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's been three.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.15,1:08:05.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Three days? The wedding is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.98,1:08:07.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.94,1:08:11.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't push it, Lupin. You'll\Nreopen your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.82,1:08:14.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I need some food. Bring me some food.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.15,1:08:16.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Food meaning what? Oatmeal?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.40,1:08:20.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm low on blood. Doesn't matter.\NJust keep it coming, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.23,1:08:24.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- That won't be so easy.\N- Don't worry. I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.36,1:08:33.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dummy, quit stuffing your face or\Nyou'll throw it all back up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.73,1:08:36.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Butt out, will ya? I'll be good as new in half a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.98,1:08:51.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I told ya, you need a bucket, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.73,1:08:54.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.07,1:08:59.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He's gotta get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.28,1:09:06.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I had no idea all of this was for Lady Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.69,1:09:08.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But with Lupin in rough shape like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.15,1:09:12.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,it would seem that you have had much\Nhistory with Lady Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.98,1:09:18.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I used to be the palace groundskeeper.\NAs a child, Lady Clarisse loved plants.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.40,1:09:22.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,When the prince and his wife passed away\Nand she was to enter the convent,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.40,1:09:24.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,she entrusted this dog to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.78,1:09:29.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So when the dog got a whiff of Lupin, he must\Nhave noticed the princess's scent.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.73,1:09:33.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But that still doesn't explain how\NLupin knew Karl's name.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.53,1:09:37.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's a lady's man. Maybe he\Ncharmed it out of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.78,1:09:38.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.15,1:09:40.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Already awake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.97,1:09:49.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It happened ten years ago. I was young and inexperienced,\Neager to set out and make a name for myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.86,1:10:00.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I did some crazy things. Real showy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.90,1:10:03.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,To top it all off, I went after the gothic bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.57,1:10:15.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I managed to pull myself up onto the shore somehow,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.40,1:10:17.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,but then I couldn't move another inch.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.34,1:10:23.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Karl? What's wrong, boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.36,1:10:36.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I really thought I had come to the end of the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.36,1:10:42.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.36,1:10:58.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Her little hands trembled as she\Nhelped me drink the water,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.48,1:11:01.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,and the ring was on her finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.90,1:11:04.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.57,1:11:06.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten all about it until I saw the ring again.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.98,1:11:16.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Fujiko's bike.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.82,1:11:19.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's a clipping from today's paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.11,1:11:23.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow an archbishop is arriving from the\NVatican for the wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.21,1:11:36.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I officially resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.65,1:11:38.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.36,1:11:42.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What? Lupin's gonna hit the wedding? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.07,1:11:45.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am. And if you're in pursuit of\NLupin, you can mobilize, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.90,1:11:48.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.36,1:12:15.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you get out of the way? We're in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.23,1:12:17.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to go. This jam\Ngoes on for miles, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.40,1:12:20.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they said there's a landslide up the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.65,1:12:22.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But isn't that any other way to get to there?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.98,1:12:24.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We'll be late for the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.36,1:12:28.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,By-golly, aren't you the fine Lord Archbishop?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.07,1:12:31.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah, just as I reckoned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.90,1:12:34.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind as to bless\Nthis little baby goat?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.82,1:12:37.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.28,1:12:40.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You're a local. Is there any other way to\Nget to Cagliostro Castle from here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.32,1:12:43.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Sure is, if-n-you don't mind country roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.82,1:12:46.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Would you show me the\Nway there? Hop in, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.69,1:12:50.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, mm-hmm. Anything to help out the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.06,1:12:59.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, men! We have to get there by nightfall!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.82,1:13:01.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,One more hill and we'll reach the border!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.36,1:13:18.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Do you think this is a good idea?\NTelevising the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.53,1:13:24.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,His Excellency wishes to show the world his wedding\Nto Lady Clarisse is a legitimate one.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.82,1:13:27.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah! His Grace, the archbishop, has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.11,1:13:36.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Do you think Lupin will show up?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.86,1:13:39.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,My shadows will be closely watching over the bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.11,1:13:42.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All your men have to do is guard the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.48,1:13:42.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.03,1:14:49.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,With light and shadow as one once more\Nit shall surely be restored.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.36,1:14:52.45,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.48,1:16:20.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The House of Cagliostro is an ancient and noble family.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.98,1:16:23.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Bring here the proof that you are the rightful heirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.30,1:16:36.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,In accordance with the old customs, the exchange\Nof rings constitute your marriage vows.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.40,1:16:45.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Daughter of the Prince of the Principality of Cagliostro,\NClarisse de Cagliostro, do your consent to this marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.69,1:16:49.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,If you do not object, respond with silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.03,1:17:11.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,May the Lord above bless you and keep you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.44,1:17:13.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I object.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.90,1:17:19.34,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,These marriage rites are profoundly tainted by greed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.32,1:17:34.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This is a curse.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.15,1:17:34.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.23,1:17:37.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,An uninvited rat's making his entrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.36,1:17:58.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I have come to speak on behalf of the\Ndead in the dungeon below.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.15,1:18:01.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I want the bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.19,1:18:03.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,We can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.90,1:18:04.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Just step back.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.15,1:18:05.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the show.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.36,1:18:12.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse, I've come for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.73,1:18:20.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Something incredible has happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.40,1:18:21.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin the Third has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.82,1:18:22.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Stop the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.94,1:18:24.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.53,1:18:26.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.36,1:18:32.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse, Clarisse, poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.23,1:18:34.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You've been drugged, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.36,1:18:37.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The rotten count drugged you so you couldn't speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.36,1:18:48.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.36,1:18:50.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You must not get closer, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.40,1:18:52.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That was foolish.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.61,1:18:55.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take care of the other two as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.69,1:18:59.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse, don't cry, Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.36,1:19:04.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.36,1:19:16.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this gift will be to your liking, Count.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.98,1:19:19.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Excellency.\N- The counterfeit bills you printed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.23,1:19:22.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Consider them my payment for the rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.36,1:19:25.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.69,1:19:26.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He's here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.53,1:19:30.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now I've got the rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.93,1:19:32.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's you, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.84,1:19:34.85,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.35,1:19:37.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,How dare you play me for a fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.94,1:19:39.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You cradle robber, don't play with fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.36,1:19:42.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Or you'll get... burned!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.66,1:19:54.37,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.02,1:20:09.51,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.36,1:20:12.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, we will now\Nresume our broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.48,1:20:15.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The wedding hall is in utter chaos.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.44,1:20:17.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Well, gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.23,1:20:18.77,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.82,1:20:27.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.36,1:20:30.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin's gotten away and the Count is hot on his heels.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.48,1:20:33.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The police have stormed the castle.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.57,1:20:37.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin's hiding under the altar.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.82,1:20:39.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Make a hole, men! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.28,1:20:44.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Zenigata's men are making a path to the altar.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.90,1:20:46.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, here's the royal guardsmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.69,1:20:48.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're led by Captain Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.03,1:20:50.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Secure the rear men.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.44,1:20:56.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Give no quarter!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.11,1:20:59.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,A fierce battle's in progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.36,1:21:02.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What secret could that altar be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.65,1:21:06.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Look, it's a staircase leading underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.69,1:21:08.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Could Lupin be hiding down in that hole?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.94,1:21:10.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's take a camera and see, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.82,1:21:13.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.03,1:21:17.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Lupin!\N- What's that imbecile doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.98,1:21:19.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He's ignoring orders, call him off!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.07,1:21:22.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Too late, it's airing live worldwide now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.40,1:21:25.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what's all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.69,1:21:27.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,This looks like a national mint!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.36,1:21:29.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Mmm, what's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.36,1:21:34.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, Japanese bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.65,1:21:35.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They must be counterfeit!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.36,1:21:37.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Talk about hamming it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.11,1:21:38.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What a find!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.23,1:21:41.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Look at this, counterfeits from everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.28,1:21:45.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I found this dreadful stuff while\NI was chasing after Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.69,1:21:46.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.16,1:22:01.21,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,First things first, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.23,1:22:02.50,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Jigen, Goemon, you good?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.53,1:22:03.54,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.57,1:22:05.25,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- We'll hold them off.\N- C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.36,1:22:12.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, I beg of you to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.11,1:22:13.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,and you Noble Jigen?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.36,1:22:16.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please make sure that you both return safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.19,1:22:18.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I will never forget your chivalry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.40,1:22:20.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You should go quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.78,1:22:24.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.07,1:22:25.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.32,1:22:35.08,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Noble Jigen.\N- Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.36,1:22:41.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's start this party.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.36,1:22:52.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Finally, my Zantetsuken has cut something meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.23,1:22:54.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Curse that Lupin, this isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.36,1:22:59.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll attend to the castle, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.11,1:23:19.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Do you still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.15,1:23:21.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm over that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.53,1:23:22.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get over this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.86,1:23:31.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Two goats facing each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.86,1:23:41.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There are gothic letters carved on the\Nseam, binding light and shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.36,1:23:44.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're too worn down to read.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.32,1:23:51.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Binding light and shadow, tolling the hours is the\Ngoat on high, and whose sun-facing eyes I belong.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.32,1:23:56.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I remember they are ancient words that were\Npassed down through my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.57,1:23:57.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Are they of help to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.98,1:23:59.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, the riddle is solved at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.66,1:24:03.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I's the Count. This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.36,1:24:12.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They are going to the machinery room. Moor the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.98,1:24:24.31,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.90,1:24:28.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.44,1:24:30.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ooh, they're coming in hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.36,1:24:38.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.94,1:24:43.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Shut down all the lasers. Does that\Nfool think they can escape?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.06,1:25:04.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- You scared?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.48,1:25:06.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.36,1:25:11.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.32,1:25:13.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.32,1:25:33.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Can't go that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.07,1:25:35.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You men go over there. Take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.73,1:25:36.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.40,1:25:45.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Okay, stay here. I'm gonna block the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.82,1:25:46.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.57,1:25:48.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Be back in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.07,1:26:00.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.86,1:26:11.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.82,1:26:13.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.09,1:26:23.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.36,1:26:30.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You missed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.90,1:26:34.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You rat! I shall skewer you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.61,1:26:36.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Take your best shot. It's your last chance, Count.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.36,1:26:59.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.36,1:27:04.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.23,1:27:16.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey! I dare you to come get me, Countypants.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.53,1:27:26.66,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.28,1:27:37.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll start by taking care of you first.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.69,1:27:39.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse, get out of here! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.78,1:28:10.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going, Clarisse?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.15,1:28:20.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come on, my dear. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.78,1:28:22.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.19,1:28:28.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And so ends the Cagliostro bloodline.\NNow die, Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.11,1:28:29.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Count. Let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.36,1:28:34.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's too late. Just stand there and\Nwatch as this woman dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.36,1:28:35.28,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.53,1:28:38.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the secret of the rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.82,1:28:41.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You can take the treasure and do\Nwhatever you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.73,1:28:44.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Just leave the girl alone. Set her free.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.15,1:28:47.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Look, the Capricorn on the clock face.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.07,1:28:50.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's the goat which faces the\Nsun and tolls the hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.98,1:28:53.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's got two holes in its eyes\Nthat the rings fit into.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.36,1:28:55.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I'll let you have the rings.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.19,1:28:58.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But if you kill Clarisse, I will\Nthrow them in the lake
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.36,1:29:00.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,and then I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.15,1:29:32.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's far enough. Let Clarisse go inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.61,1:29:35.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,All right. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.36,1:29:46.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, you have to hold your winning\Ncard to the final hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.36,1:29:49.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.69,1:29:56.73,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,They're the genuine articles this\Ntime and now they're mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.83,1:29:59.60,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here's your payment for solving the riddle, Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.36,1:30:01.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.36,1:30:05.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.70,1:30:11.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.43,1:30:11.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Clarisse!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.36,1:31:42.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah! The clock tower!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.36,1:31:54.98,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Ah! Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.36,1:32:32.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.36,1:33:02.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Count Cagliostro's reign is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.90,1:33:04.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.57,1:33:07.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, I will not take your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.69,1:34:00.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,- Monsieur.\N- Hey, can you stand? Feast your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.55,1:34:25.70,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The real hidden treasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.36,1:34:29.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I had no idea there was a Roman city beneath the lake.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.15,1:34:35.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,When the Romans were driven from this land, they\Nbuilt that floodgate and submerged it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.61,1:34:38.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,And your ancestors quietly inherited it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.48,1:34:45.11,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.07,1:34:51.23,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,It's amazing. A treasure that belongs\Nto all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.65,1:34:53.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no way it'll fit in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.36,1:35:13.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Interpol finally sprang into action.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.36,1:35:31.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Will you be leaving now?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.53,1:35:35.36,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah. A lot of scary men just showed up, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.03,1:35:42.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please, take me with you. I don't have the\Nskills of a thief, but I can learn.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.44,1:35:44.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, I want to...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.53,1:35:48.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Please, I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.07,1:35:52.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.36,1:36:04.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Now, don't give me that silly talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.36,1:36:06.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You don't want to go back into the darkness again,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.61,1:36:09.82,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,when it took you so long to find your\Nway to the sunlight, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.03,1:36:12.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You belong right here. Your whole\Nlife is just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.19,1:36:15.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,The life of a thief is no life for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.07,1:36:18.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,But if you're ever in trouble, call me anytime,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.40,1:36:21.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,and I will come running, even if it's from the\Nfar reaches of the Earth, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.78,1:36:33.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Karl, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.90,1:36:35.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Karl!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.94,1:36:37.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lady Clarisse.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.94,1:36:38.65,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hi, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.22,1:36:51.15,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Toodles Clarisse!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.15,1:36:51.93,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.57,1:36:53.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So long, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.44,1:36:57.53,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Wait, Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.07,1:37:00.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Bye, Clarisse. You take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.86,1:37:01.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Goodbye now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.36,1:37:06.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone. So long.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.19,1:37:07.86,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.40,1:37:12.12,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Goodbye. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.23,1:37:26.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Darn. Just missed him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.48,1:37:28.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He got away with another treasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.78,1:37:30.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't steal anything, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.07,1:37:33.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,He saved my life and fought for my honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.78,1:37:36.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,No, Miss. He ran off with a tremendous\Nprize in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.57,1:37:39.32,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Your heart, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.36,1:37:42.61,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.61,1:37:45.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Well then. Good day, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.11,1:37:53.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,After Lupin, to the ends of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.36,1:38:15.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,What an intriguing bunch of fellows they were.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.78,1:38:20.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,I feel as though I have known that gentleman\Nfrom a very long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.07,1:38:24.48,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin, I know we'll meet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.40,1:38:32.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,She was a nice girl, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.11,1:38:36.94,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You know, Lupin, you could stay here if you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.90,1:38:42.19,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Fujicakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.53,1:38:44.44,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lupin. Take a look at what I scored.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.98,1:38:47.90,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hmm? The master printing plate's\Nfor the counterfeit bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.15,1:38:49.57,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,That's great. Let me have one.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.07,1:38:50.78,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.23,1:38:52.69,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.69,1:38:55.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Hey, just hold on a sec. We could trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.02,1:39:00.07,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Here comes Pops. He never gives up.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.15,1:39:03.03,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,You won't get away this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.86,1:39:04.40,Default-Discotek,,0,0,0,,Lupin!
